longBusinessSummary: Petrox Resources Corp., a junior oil and gas company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, development, and production of petroleum and natural gas resources in the Western Canadian Basin. The company owns a production property located in Fletwode, Saskatchewan. Petrox Resources Corp. was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Calgary, Canada.
